column4: Hi I am having a problem with my speakers. Sound is not being emitted, but I know it's not a hardware problem. Does anyone here know what i can do to fix this problem?
make sure the necessary mixer sliders are unmuted.
does cat /proc/asound/cards list your sound card?
post amixer output onto http://pastebin.ca
no, I mean the output from ,,amixer'' (without the commas and quotes)
